　　Ris sia Sophia,Riris ele,elmei Selab pheno sia-s——Co lue-l-Sophie nett
　　黎明之歌是邂逅·那首歌一定能传送到你身边
　　Ris sia Sophia,Neight ele,elmei Kyels riss Sepah cela-s——Sophit ele Ende